== Colored Inventory Items for wow Classic ==

This addon will add colored border items for :
- character pane
- inspect pane
- bags
- bank
- merchant frame
- professions

In bags and bank, items with green quality and more will have a colored border according their quality.
Quest items are also colorized with a yellow border.

Type /cii for configuration. You will be able to disable border display for specific frame group 
in case you got addon taht already manage this feature (like bagnon for bags).

For more information https://gitlab.com/sigz/ColoredInventoryItems
